    affiliation: University of Waterloo
repository-code: "https://github.com/SamSi0322/ResearchOS"
url: "https://github.com/SamSi0322/ResearchOS"
license: AGPL-3.0
abstract: >
  ResearchOS is a local-first research decision and execution system. It turns a
  research brief into runnable experiments, evidence-checked claims, and a
  packaged manuscript draft, with provider-agnostic LLM adapters and human-in-the-loop
  approval gates. Runs entirely on localhost.
keywords:
  - research
  - decision-support
  - llm
  - large-language-models
  - reproducibility
  - python
  - fastapi
  - local-first
